1
00:00:01,010 --> 00:00:03,850
<i>LOVE AND REDEMPTION</i>

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:06,640
<i>EPISODE 6</i>

3
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:22,832
No.

4
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:25,888
I can’t let this dummy
continue to sleep here.

5
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,879
Don’t go.

6
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:59,648
Don’t leave me behind.

7
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:42,239
I never thought that the secret ground
of Shaoyang Sect

8
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:44,399
will be guarded so heavily.

9
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:46,606
It has taken me a lot of work.

10
00:02:46,607 --> 00:02:50,080
But no matter how well-guarded
it is, I still found it in the end.

11
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,925
Someone has broken into the secret ground.

12
00:02:56,926 --> 00:02:58,049
Hurry!

13
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:06,759
This is the ancient Candle Dragon?

14
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:10,359
I never thought that they’ll use
the Candle Dragon to guard a spirit key.

15
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:13,361
Darn it. Is Ling Shi
trying to get me killed?

16
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:19,157
The barrier is intact.

17
00:03:19,158 --> 00:03:21,918
I wonder who’s the one that
broke into the secret ground again.

18
00:03:22,462 --> 00:03:24,368
Luckily, you and your master have already

19
00:03:24,369 --> 00:03:26,605
reinforced this barrier before this.

20
00:03:26,606 --> 00:03:29,962
Even the curious ones will not
be able to get pass Candle Dragon.

21
00:03:29,963 --> 00:03:32,890
I’ll lay down a few more
Defensive Formations with Uncle Lu Yang

22
00:03:32,891 --> 00:03:35,170
to prevent anyone from
getting near to this place.

23
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:13,600
Shi Feng from Xuanyuan Sect wins.

24
00:04:25,815 --> 00:04:29,679
How did Xuanyuan Sect
become so powerful this year?

25
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,713
It’s quite strange.

26
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,494
Si Feng!

27
00:04:39,495 --> 00:04:41,359
All the best, Si Feng!

28
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,040
You have to win!

29
00:04:49,479 --> 00:04:50,879
Wu Tong.

30
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,478
Remember this.

31
00:04:52,479 --> 00:04:55,405
I made the exception to accept you
because you looked so sincere.

32
00:04:55,942 --> 00:05:01,461
If you can’t come first
this time, you can leave us.

33
00:05:01,462 --> 00:05:03,187
I’ll definitely get the first place.

34
00:05:07,660 --> 00:05:10,429
All the best, Si Feng!
Si Feng, defeat him!

35
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,518
Si Feng!

36
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,555
All the best!

37
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,805
Great!

38
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:27,044
It’s a spell again!

39
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:40,766
I remember that I already
said this the last time.

40
00:06:40,767 --> 00:06:42,479
Spell is not allowed.

41
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:44,144
I can forgive you the first time.

42
00:06:44,145 --> 00:06:46,079
But second time is unforgivable.

43
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:47,229
Wu Tong.

44
00:06:47,230 --> 00:06:49,685
You already broke the rule just now.

45
00:06:49,686 --> 00:06:53,600
I think this round should go
to Yu Si Feng from Lize Palace.

46
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:01,203
You useless thing! Are you that incapable?

47
00:07:01,204 --> 00:07:02,999
If you can’t come first, you can leave us.

48
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:05,846
Master, I still have other skills.

49
00:07:05,847 --> 00:07:08,276
Sect Leader Chu, let me compete again.

50
00:07:08,277 --> 00:07:10,359
Yu Si Feng did not defeat me.
I didn’t lose.

51
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:13,039
You broke the rule and you still
want to compete. You have no shame.

52
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:15,119
Does Dianjinggu Sect have no rules?

53
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,997
- You...
- Say no more.

54
00:07:16,998 --> 00:07:18,875
Dianjinggu Sect has lost

55
00:07:20,558 --> 00:07:22,061
in this round.

56
00:07:22,062 --> 00:07:24,719
Master!

57
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:27,080
Sect Leader Chu, let me compete again!

58
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:31,197
Tell me.

59
00:07:31,198 --> 00:07:34,449
Do you know how to write the word dignity?

60
00:07:34,450 --> 00:07:36,719
- Shut up!
- I...

61
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:38,274
Forget it. He’s so fierce.

62
00:07:38,275 --> 00:07:39,759
- Let him be.
- It’s okay. Let me.

63
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,759
Even your master has already
asked you to leave.

64
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:43,404
Why are you still here?

65
00:07:44,662 --> 00:07:47,439
Since you like to talk so
much, I’ll shut you up forever.

66
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,720
Be careful!

67
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,200
Xuan Ji!

68
00:08:11,030 --> 00:08:12,876
Don’t be too arrogant.

69
00:08:13,446 --> 00:08:15,206
Try dying.

70
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,662
Stop right there!

71
00:08:54,663 --> 00:08:56,106
Don’t run!

72
00:09:11,323 --> 00:09:13,325
Chase after him! Don’t let him run away!

73
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,563
Stop right there!

74
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:27,014
How is she?

75
00:09:27,015 --> 00:09:29,885
I’ve patched up her artery.
She should be fine now.

76
00:09:29,886 --> 00:09:31,439
I’ll perform acupuncture on her later.

77
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:34,919
But Aunt Ying Hong, why
is she still unconscious?

78
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:37,325
She was bleeding so much just now.

79
00:09:37,326 --> 00:09:39,047
Ling Long, calm down first.

80
00:09:39,048 --> 00:09:41,349
Master Ying Hong
has said that she’ll be fine.

81
00:09:41,350 --> 00:09:42,990
Xuan Ji will definitely wake up.

82
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,799
It’s all because of Wu Tong.

83
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:48,479
We have to find Wu Tong to avenge her!

84
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,618
Enough.

85
00:09:50,653 --> 00:09:52,734
Stop disturbing your aunt.

86
00:09:53,391 --> 00:09:54,719
Let’s go out first.

87
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,141
Aunt Ying Hong.

88
00:09:56,142 --> 00:09:57,460
She’ll be fine.

89
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:08,720
<i>SHOUYANG HALL</i>

90
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:13,173
Sect Leader, we’re incapable.
Wu Tong got away.

91
00:10:13,174 --> 00:10:14,485
What?

92
00:10:16,166 --> 00:10:18,942
Barricade all exits right now.
Don’t let him get away!

93
00:10:18,943 --> 00:10:20,104
Yes!

94
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:24,400
Brother Chu, how is Xuan Ji?

95
00:10:27,235 --> 00:10:28,948
Luckily, she’s not fatally wounded.

96
00:10:28,949 --> 00:10:31,808
But we don’t know when she will wake up.

97
00:10:33,519 --> 00:10:34,886
Sect Leader Chu.

98
00:10:34,887 --> 00:10:38,901
I’m really ashamed for
what happened today.

99
00:10:38,902 --> 00:10:42,681
I have a high-quality medicine for wound
that is passed down by our great master.

100
00:10:42,682 --> 00:10:44,934
Later, I’ll ask my disciple to
send it to her.

101
00:10:44,935 --> 00:10:47,695
Hopefully, it can help with her wound.

102
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:53,022
It’s Dianjinggu Sect’s fault for
not educating my disciple well.

103
00:10:53,023 --> 00:10:56,442
That Wu Tong came to me out of the blue.

104
00:10:56,443 --> 00:10:59,275
I wanted to lead him into the lights.
But I never thought that

105
00:10:59,276 --> 00:11:01,172
he would bring such disaster today.

106
00:11:01,173 --> 00:11:04,839
If that’s the case,
Dianjinggu Sect will no longer keep him.

107
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:07,507
Today, I’m going to kick Wu Tong out
from Dianjinggu Sect

108
00:11:07,508 --> 00:11:10,079
in front of every sect here.

109
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:14,055
From now on, Wu Tong and Dianjinggu Sect
are no longer related.

110
00:11:14,056 --> 00:11:16,740
You are really good at passing the buck,
Valley Master Rong.

111
00:11:19,342 --> 00:11:21,429
You might have kicked him out.

112
00:11:21,430 --> 00:11:24,350
But what about
the competition ranking then?

113
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,713
To make up for all of you,

114
00:11:26,714 --> 00:11:29,893
Dianjinggu will withdraw from
the competition this time.

115
00:11:29,894 --> 00:11:32,845
It’s a form of apology too.

116
00:11:32,846 --> 00:11:35,359
Although Wu Tong has been
kicked out from Dianjinggu,

117
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:37,853
he seriously wounded Xuan Ji
and escaped to avoid punishment.

118
00:11:37,854 --> 00:11:39,774
We can’t let him off the hook so easily.

119
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:42,703
No matter where he runs,

120
00:11:42,704 --> 00:11:45,581
I’ll definitely catch him
and bring him to justice.

121
00:11:45,582 --> 00:11:47,830
Wu Tong is bad-tempered and vicious.

122
00:11:47,831 --> 00:11:50,799
If we let him run loose,
he’ll be a disaster to the people.

123
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:53,759
In order to uphold justice,
we have the responsibility

124
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:55,447
to get rid of him for the people.

125
00:11:55,448 --> 00:11:58,952
If that’s the case, Dianjinggu
Sect will take the lead first.

126
00:11:59,550 --> 00:12:02,953
From today onwards,
Dianjinggu Sect, Shaoyang Sect,

127
00:12:02,954 --> 00:12:06,064
Lize Palace, Xuanyuan Sect and Fuyu Island

128
00:12:06,065 --> 00:12:09,439
will work together to arrest Wu Tong.

129
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:12,326
If there is any resistant
or people harbouring him,

130
00:12:12,327 --> 00:12:15,376
they’ll be going against us five sects!

131
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:31,269
<i>REWARD: 500 SILVER FOR WU TONG</i>

132
00:12:36,158 --> 00:12:37,679
Wait.

133
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:38,909
Go.

134
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:44,110
<i>WANTED; REWARD: 500 SILVER</i>

135
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:02,400
The first pupil of Lize Palace
is really kind.

136
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:07,840
You even withdrew from
the Flower Session for a girl.

137
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:13,909
Chu Xuan Ji was seriously wounded by
Wu Tong because she defended

138
00:13:13,910 --> 00:13:16,301
me during the competition.

139
00:13:16,302 --> 00:13:19,448
Now, she is still unconscious and
her life might still be in danger.

140
00:13:19,449 --> 00:13:22,489
Out of moral responsibility,
how can I not show care towards her?

141
00:13:26,375 --> 00:13:28,895
What a noble and honourable excuse.

142
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:31,446
Yu Si Feng.

143
00:13:31,447 --> 00:13:34,319
You are the first pupil that
the palace lord has high hope in.

144
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:36,994
You have to fight for
Lize Palace’s reputation.

145
00:13:36,995 --> 00:13:40,894
If you don’t want to make up for
your mistake for losing your mask

146
00:13:40,895 --> 00:13:43,314
by becoming first in the Flower Session,

147
00:13:44,750 --> 00:13:46,310
so be it.

148
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,877
Is Xuan Ji getting better?

149
00:14:00,878 --> 00:14:04,519
Aunt Ying Hong said that she’ll wake up
after resting for two days.

150
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:06,839
Si Feng, take care of Xuan Ji
for us first.

151
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:08,773
We’ll go and fetch the medicine for her.

152
00:14:08,774 --> 00:14:09,885
Let’s go.

153
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,640
Xuan Ji.

154
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:40,829
Xuan Ji!

155
00:14:44,231 --> 00:14:45,505
Who are you?

156
00:15:16,447 --> 00:15:17,718
Xuan Ji.

157
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:20,360
When are you going to wake up?

158
00:15:21,647 --> 00:15:24,358
I’m afraid that I’ll have to
go back to Lize Palace

159
00:15:24,359 --> 00:15:26,164
before I can bid my farewell with you.

160
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:30,280
Do you know that if you
can wake up and smile,

161
00:15:30,800 --> 00:15:35,823
I’ll be able to go through
any hardships when I go back?

162
00:15:50,782 --> 00:15:54,629
Hero Yu, you are so kind for
coming here every day

163
00:15:54,630 --> 00:15:56,204
to take care of Xuan Ji.

164
00:15:57,229 --> 00:16:01,029
Thank you for saving
the junior of our sect twice.

165
00:16:01,030 --> 00:16:02,522
I never thought that

166
00:16:02,523 --> 00:16:05,342
there is still a righteous disciple
like you in Lize Palace.

167
00:16:06,319 --> 00:16:08,045
Xuan Ji is my friend.

168
00:16:08,046 --> 00:16:09,748
I can’t do much.

169
00:16:09,749 --> 00:16:12,751
I just hope that she can wake up soon.

170
00:16:12,752 --> 00:16:14,547
Don’t worry. She will.

171
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:37,349
This is weird.
She was so seriously wounded.

172
00:16:37,350 --> 00:16:40,125
But she’s almost healed although
it has just been a few days.

173
00:16:40,126 --> 00:16:41,941
It’s really surprising.

174
00:16:49,720 --> 00:16:51,428
She has indeed recovered very quickly.

175
00:16:51,429 --> 00:16:53,479
We’ve given her a lot of
medicine and supplements

176
00:16:53,480 --> 00:16:55,444
from various sects for the past few days.

177
00:16:55,445 --> 00:16:57,827
They must have helped her recovered.

178
00:16:57,828 --> 00:17:01,949
Although she looks fine now,
she has lost a lot of blood.

179
00:17:01,950 --> 00:17:04,030
I think she’ll still be unconscious
for a while.

180
00:17:05,009 --> 00:17:06,479
As long as she is fine.

181
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:09,799
Xuan Ji is a very fortunate person.

182
00:17:12,398 --> 00:17:13,743
Yu Si Feng.

183
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:16,767
Vice Palace Lord.

184
00:17:17,360 --> 00:17:19,519
You still know that
I’m the vice palace lord?

185
00:17:19,520 --> 00:17:21,177
I haven’t seen you for so many days.

186
00:17:21,178 --> 00:17:24,219
I thought you’ve already forgotten about
Lize Palace’s rules.

187
00:17:24,805 --> 00:17:26,005
I wouldn’t dare.

188
00:17:26,903 --> 00:17:28,639
You need to focus.

189
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:30,159
And pack your things too.

190
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:31,879
Get ready to go back.

191
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:33,084
Vice Palace Lord.

192
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:36,240
The Flower Session is not over yet, right?

193
00:17:37,014 --> 00:17:38,725
The game is already set.

194
00:17:38,726 --> 00:17:41,046
Xuanyuan Sect got lucky this time.

195
00:17:42,040 --> 00:17:44,310
Lize Palace is really noble.

196
00:17:44,311 --> 00:17:46,653
We just gave away
the first place to others.

197
00:17:46,654 --> 00:17:49,303
Nobody cares about that Flower Session.

198
00:17:50,414 --> 00:17:53,214
What is it? Are you reluctant to leave?

199
00:17:55,718 --> 00:17:57,301
No.

200
00:17:57,302 --> 00:18:00,229
I just think that if we leave like that,

201
00:18:00,230 --> 00:18:02,630
it’ll look like Lize Palace
is a sore loser.

202
00:18:03,519 --> 00:18:05,061
Vice Palace Lord.

203
00:18:05,062 --> 00:18:08,012
How about we wait for a few more days?

204
00:18:09,174 --> 00:18:11,742
Don’t think that I don’t know
what you are thinking about.

205
00:18:13,046 --> 00:18:15,639
Forget it. You are not my problem.

206
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:17,294
You are the palace lord’s disciple.

207
00:18:17,295 --> 00:18:19,463
He’ll punish you when you go back.

208
00:18:19,998 --> 00:18:23,094
Your days of freedom
will come to an end soon.

209
00:18:23,095 --> 00:18:27,401
I understand that you want
to cherish your remaining time.

210
00:18:48,480 --> 00:18:49,895
Xuan Ji.

211
00:18:51,520 --> 00:18:53,849
In the end,
I still can’t wait until you wake up.

212
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:56,430
I don’t know if you can hear me.

213
00:18:56,431 --> 00:18:58,487
But I still want to tell you that

214
00:18:58,488 --> 00:19:01,488
it’s the happiest thing in my life to be
able to come out

215
00:19:03,110 --> 00:19:04,838
and meet you here.

216
00:19:06,920 --> 00:19:08,956
I’ll remember our four-year promise.

217
00:19:10,120 --> 00:19:13,462
No matter how hard
it is, we’ll meet again.

218
00:19:14,520 --> 00:19:16,199
Si Feng.

219
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:17,378
You are leaving?

220
00:19:19,120 --> 00:19:21,388
The Flower Session has ended
for a few days already.

221
00:19:21,389 --> 00:19:22,372
I can’t extend my stay anymore.

222
00:19:22,373 --> 00:19:25,255
Xuan Ji will be sad when
she wakes up with you gone.

223
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:30,101
The sound of this bell
can travel for miles.

224
00:19:30,102 --> 00:19:33,133
Ling Long, please give this to her for me.

225
00:19:33,134 --> 00:19:35,925
She can contact me with it
when she wakes up.

226
00:19:35,926 --> 00:19:37,401
Don’t forget about it.

227
00:19:37,402 --> 00:19:39,877
Don’t worry. I’ll tell her.

228
00:19:39,878 --> 00:19:41,964
Too bad we haven’t caught Wu Tong yet.

229
00:19:41,965 --> 00:19:45,680
Or else, we can watch him get
punished to uphold justice for Xuan Ji.

230
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:49,731
I still think that this matter
is not handled properly.

231
00:19:50,446 --> 00:19:52,279
Wu Tong is just a normal disciple.

232
00:19:52,280 --> 00:19:56,358
But now, the five sects work together
to make him a wanted criminal.

233
00:19:56,359 --> 00:19:59,485
He should’ve thought of that
when he hurt Xuan Ji back then.

234
00:19:59,486 --> 00:20:01,846
He has only himself to blame.

235
00:20:02,629 --> 00:20:04,119
I didn’t mean that.

236
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:07,261
Wu Tong is very narrow-minded
and he’s an extremist.

237
00:20:07,262 --> 00:20:09,774
It’s not a good thing to corner him.

238
00:20:09,775 --> 00:20:11,599
Or maybe I think too much.

239
00:20:11,600 --> 00:20:14,468
Ling Long, Min Yan, take care.

240
00:20:14,469 --> 00:20:17,066
- Farewell.
- You too, my brother.

241
00:20:17,067 --> 00:20:19,822
After Xuan Ji is awake,
we’ll go and visit you at Lize Palace.

242
00:20:42,360 --> 00:20:45,965
Bring Yu Si Feng, the disciple
who broke the rule into the hall!

243
00:20:49,560 --> 00:20:52,380
<i>LIZE PALACE</i>

244
00:21:03,758 --> 00:21:05,079
Yu Si Feng.

245
00:21:05,080 --> 00:21:07,029
As the first pupil of Lize Palace and

246
00:21:07,030 --> 00:21:09,159
as the preferred successor
of the palace lord,

247
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:12,479
not only you are not strict with yourself
and be a role model to everyone,

248
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:15,037
you even lost your mask outside
and showed your real face.

249
00:21:15,038 --> 00:21:19,119
You broke the rule and put
Lize Palace in danger.

250
00:21:19,120 --> 00:21:21,454
Do you know what is
the punishment you deserve?

251
00:21:24,775 --> 00:21:26,677
The 13 Punishments.

252
00:21:26,678 --> 00:21:28,573
I accept the punishments
with no objection.

253
00:21:28,574 --> 00:21:30,622
Take away his First Pupil Token and

254
00:21:30,623 --> 00:21:32,919
send him into the 13 Punishments
Lianyu Pagoda at once.

255
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:34,251
Wait.

256
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:41,566
This is the first time
he committed this mistake.

257
00:21:41,567 --> 00:21:45,347
Besides, he didn’t do it on purpose.
He had a solid reason.

258
00:21:45,348 --> 00:21:49,087
This is not a suitable punishment.

259
00:21:50,200 --> 00:21:53,902
When I was cultivating myself
two years ago in seclusion,

260
00:21:53,903 --> 00:21:57,982
Si Feng had attended to me diligently.

261
00:21:57,983 --> 00:21:59,837
He had made great contributions.

262
00:21:59,838 --> 00:22:02,622
I haven’t even rewarded him yet.

263
00:22:02,623 --> 00:22:05,589
He made a mistake this time.
But his merit offsets fault.

264
00:22:05,590 --> 00:22:07,410
As for his reward and punishment,

265
00:22:09,798 --> 00:22:11,814
they’ve cancelled each other out.

266
00:22:11,815 --> 00:22:13,085
Palace Lord.

267
00:22:14,360 --> 00:22:16,559
Based on Lize Palace’s centuries of rules,

268
00:22:16,560 --> 00:22:19,359
if a disciple lost his mask and
showed his true face outside,

269
00:22:19,360 --> 00:22:21,762
he has to be sent into
the 13 Punishments Lianyu Pagoda.

270
00:22:21,763 --> 00:22:23,373
Even though he made a contribution,

271
00:22:23,374 --> 00:22:27,229
you still have to discuss it first with
two other palace lords and four elders.

272
00:22:27,230 --> 00:22:29,747
How can you just cancel out
the punishment like that?

273
00:22:30,614 --> 00:22:35,181
Looks like the palace lord is being
biased towards his own disciple.

274
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:46,870
What is it?

275
00:22:46,871 --> 00:22:51,485
Are you saying that his merit for
helping me out in my cultivation

276
00:22:51,486 --> 00:22:54,406
is not enough to cancel out
the punishment for losing the mask?

277
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:59,143
Losing his mask is not
the only rule he broke.

278
00:22:59,144 --> 00:23:02,640
He’s very close with those disciples
from Shaoyang Sect.

279
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:07,639
And his relationship with that Chu Xuan Ji

280
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:10,567
is not just a simple friendship.

281
00:23:10,568 --> 00:23:13,805
He even withdrew from
the Flower Session for her

282
00:23:13,806 --> 00:23:18,029
and let Lize Palace lost the chance
to become the head of the five sects.

283
00:23:18,030 --> 00:23:20,045
Where does this rumour come from?

284
00:23:21,040 --> 00:23:22,559
Impossible.

285
00:23:22,560 --> 00:23:24,400
This is not true.

286
00:23:28,030 --> 00:23:30,794
Profound sentiments of friendship.

287
00:23:31,799 --> 00:23:33,919
I think he said it himself.

288
00:23:35,324 --> 00:23:37,881
Yu Si Feng, do you remember?

289
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:41,190
Yes, I do.

290
00:23:42,175 --> 00:23:46,580
My feelings for Xuan Ji is
indeed more than friendship.

291
00:23:47,560 --> 00:23:49,326
I don’t want to lie.

292
00:23:51,520 --> 00:23:52,895
Yu Si Feng!

293
00:24:03,280 --> 00:24:06,479
I think you’ve been
possessed by an outsider.

294
00:24:06,480 --> 00:24:07,919
Say it.

295
00:24:07,920 --> 00:24:09,908
Say that you are sorry.

296
00:24:13,081 --> 00:24:16,519
You have been bewitched because
you are young and ignorant.

297
00:24:16,520 --> 00:24:19,212
Say it! Say that you are sorry!

298
00:24:24,640 --> 00:24:26,479
He won’t say it.

299
00:24:26,480 --> 00:24:27,719
Palace Lord.

300
00:24:27,720 --> 00:24:30,526
A disciple of Lize Palace can never
fall in love with a woman

301
00:24:30,527 --> 00:24:33,079
and can never have a wife and family.

302
00:24:33,080 --> 00:24:36,086
As the first pupil of Lize Palace,
he lost to temptation

303
00:24:36,087 --> 00:24:38,999
and was influenced by an outside woman.
He destroyed his own future.

304
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:41,719
He has broken many rules.
His punishment cannot be cancelled.

305
00:24:41,720 --> 00:24:45,406
Palace Lord, he has to be sent into
the 13 Punishments Lianyu Pagoda!

306
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:49,357
Shut up!

307
00:24:54,240 --> 00:24:57,239
What kind of a place that
13 Punishments Lianyu Pagoda is?

308
00:24:57,240 --> 00:25:03,842
Since ancient times, how many
did come out alive after going in?

309
00:25:03,843 --> 00:25:05,525
Moreover,

310
00:25:05,526 --> 00:25:09,931
Si Feng is a rare talent that only
appears once in a blue moon.

311
00:25:10,670 --> 00:25:12,593
Don’t you know that?

312
00:25:13,120 --> 00:25:15,886
I still want to teach him well

313
00:25:17,128 --> 00:25:19,639
and let him bring pride to Lize Palace!

314
00:25:19,640 --> 00:25:23,399
If he goes through the 13
Punishments and dies inside it,

315
00:25:23,400 --> 00:25:28,346
who will be able to lead
Lize Palace in the future?

316
00:25:29,720 --> 00:25:31,437
Palace Lord.

317
00:25:31,438 --> 00:25:34,199
If he can’t survive
the 13 Punishments Lianyu Pagoda,

318
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:38,094
how can he be the rare talent
of Lize Palace?

319
00:25:39,029 --> 00:25:40,639
If you really want to be biased,

320
00:25:40,640 --> 00:25:43,830
we won’t be able to enforce the rules
of Lize Palace in the future.

321
00:25:43,831 --> 00:25:45,471
Shut up.

322
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:53,311
Palace Lord.

323
00:25:53,312 --> 00:25:57,207
The rules of Lize Palace
are set by our great ancestors.

324
00:25:57,208 --> 00:26:01,688
Palace lords needs to discuss with
the elders before any decision is made.

325
00:26:02,480 --> 00:26:05,720
The palace lord has no rights
to make the decision alone.

326
00:26:06,622 --> 00:26:08,039
I’m having a headache.

327
00:26:08,040 --> 00:26:09,840
Terrible headache.

328
00:26:13,455 --> 00:26:16,662
I can’t discuss this further today.

329
00:26:16,663 --> 00:26:22,439
Take him into the prison first
and we’ll discuss it on another day.

330
00:26:22,440 --> 00:26:25,199
Palace Lord, we have to make
a decision eventually!

331
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:28,036
Palace Lord, it’ll be hard to
convince everyone if we do this!

332
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:31,446
Take Yu Si Feng into the prison first.

333
00:26:41,191 --> 00:26:43,725
A decision has to be made eventually.

334
00:26:43,726 --> 00:26:46,206
How long can he delay this?

335
00:26:59,966 --> 00:27:01,264
Brother Liu.

336
00:27:03,800 --> 00:27:05,369
Little Phoenix.

337
00:27:06,360 --> 00:27:07,971
What happened?

338
00:27:10,360 --> 00:27:12,679
You brat.

339
00:27:12,680 --> 00:27:15,120
I was still hoping that
you can bring some wine for me.

340
00:27:15,629 --> 00:27:19,159
Now, you are locked up by
those two monsters as well.

341
00:27:19,160 --> 00:27:22,639
No. You are the best disciple
in Lize Palace.

342
00:27:22,640 --> 00:27:26,247
Your eccentric master
dotes on you the most, right?

343
00:27:26,840 --> 00:27:28,279
It’s not his fault.

344
00:27:28,280 --> 00:27:31,349
I’m the one who took off
my mask and broke the rules.

345
00:27:32,920 --> 00:27:36,268
Mask again. I can’t believe Lize Palace.

346
00:27:36,269 --> 00:27:39,191
Why are they always so violent
about one mask?

347
00:27:39,880 --> 00:27:43,964
They always say that only the disciples
in the palace are your family.

348
00:27:43,965 --> 00:27:47,061
But actually,
this is just an inhumane place.

349
00:27:48,933 --> 00:27:52,646
But you always followed
the rules by the book, right?

350
00:27:52,647 --> 00:27:54,341
Why did you take off your mask?

351
00:27:54,342 --> 00:27:57,383
Did it fell down by itself or
someone took it off?

352
00:28:05,127 --> 00:28:07,167
Something is wrong with you.

353
00:28:09,502 --> 00:28:10,742
Wait.

354
00:28:20,920 --> 00:28:22,679
Brother Liu.

355
00:28:22,680 --> 00:28:23,639
This is...

356
00:28:23,640 --> 00:28:25,443
Spell of deceit.

357
00:28:25,444 --> 00:28:28,517
I’ve been here for so many years.
Of course I have to do something.

358
00:28:29,120 --> 00:28:33,318
Let me tell you. I’ve cleared a path
through all the prison rooms here.

359
00:28:33,319 --> 00:28:34,573
Look.

360
00:28:35,560 --> 00:28:39,879
The prison of Lize Palace
is built on the Kushui River

361
00:28:39,880 --> 00:28:43,640
and the bottom of it is surrounded
by bitter water that we can’t survive in.

362
00:28:43,641 --> 00:28:46,155
It looks very well-guarded. But it’s not.

363
00:28:46,156 --> 00:28:50,519
I’ve dug a secret tunnel
that I can escape with.

364
00:28:50,520 --> 00:28:54,398
Nothing is too hard for me.

365
00:28:54,399 --> 00:28:59,062
So, you always sneaked
out to see your daughter.

366
00:28:59,760 --> 00:29:04,309
You can sneak out but you
continue to be locked inside here.

367
00:29:04,310 --> 00:29:05,951
It’s for your daughter, right?

368
00:29:09,829 --> 00:29:14,494
I heard that the old palace lord
once forced you to make a vow

369
00:29:14,495 --> 00:29:16,479
on your daughter’s life.

370
00:29:16,480 --> 00:29:19,536
That’s why you are stuck here for decades.

371
00:29:22,743 --> 00:29:24,085
Yes.

372
00:29:24,086 --> 00:29:25,807
If it wasn’t for Yu’Er...

373
00:29:31,294 --> 00:29:32,599
Don’t talk about me.

374
00:29:32,600 --> 00:29:34,166
Let’s talk about you.

375
00:29:34,167 --> 00:29:37,173
What happened to your mask?
Who took it off?

376
00:29:37,174 --> 00:29:38,564
Was it a boy or girl?

377
00:29:39,920 --> 00:29:41,492
Is she beautiful?

378
00:29:44,600 --> 00:29:46,203
You are getting shy.

379
00:29:47,320 --> 00:29:50,354
Come. Let’s drink while we talk.

380
00:29:55,960 --> 00:29:57,137
Here.

381
00:29:59,279 --> 00:30:01,018
Take it and drink it.

382
00:30:04,429 --> 00:30:09,359
Brother Liu, since young,
whenever I saw you in prison,

383
00:30:09,360 --> 00:30:13,700
you would always trick others to drink
in order to uncover others’ secret.

384
00:30:14,351 --> 00:30:17,000
That part of you has never changed.

385
00:30:18,120 --> 00:30:21,351
But you are the only one who will
tell me about the outside world.

386
00:30:22,591 --> 00:30:24,213
You always said that

387
00:30:24,214 --> 00:30:27,365
humans’ feelings are
troublesome and complicated.

388
00:30:27,366 --> 00:30:29,461
But they are also the most beautiful.

389
00:30:29,462 --> 00:30:30,533
I think...

390
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:33,040
I understand now.

391
00:30:35,527 --> 00:30:37,170
Little Phoenix.

392
00:30:37,171 --> 00:30:39,445
You always look so cold.

393
00:30:39,446 --> 00:30:43,046
But I know that you are the most
open-minded person.

394
00:30:43,047 --> 00:30:45,881
You look a little bit like me in the past.

395
00:30:45,882 --> 00:30:47,965
You met a girl you like, right?

396
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:02,988
No.

397
00:31:02,989 --> 00:31:04,748
If you had just taken off your mask,

398
00:31:04,749 --> 00:31:08,734
based on your position in the palace
and how defensive your master is,

399
00:31:09,320 --> 00:31:11,493
your master will definitely
do everything he can

400
00:31:11,494 --> 00:31:13,432
to cancel off your punishment.

401
00:31:15,172 --> 00:31:19,094
But it’ll be troublesome if you have
really admitted that you like someone.

402
00:31:19,958 --> 00:31:22,999
I don’t think you’ll be able to
escape the 13 Punishments.

403
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:25,570
When that time comes,
even your master can’t protect you.

404
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:29,672
You haven’t admitted this
to those old-fashioned men, right?

405
00:31:31,200 --> 00:31:33,078
I can’t lie to my master.

406
00:31:33,079 --> 00:31:35,231
And I cannot deceive my own heart.

407
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:38,966
You are quite smart usually.

408
00:31:38,967 --> 00:31:41,159
Why are you acting dumb at time like this?

409
00:31:41,160 --> 00:31:43,959
Do you know what kind of place
13 Punishments Lianyu Pagoda is?

410
00:31:43,960 --> 00:31:45,428
I know.

411
00:31:45,429 --> 00:31:48,547
I broke the rules.
I’m willing to be punished.

412
00:31:48,548 --> 00:31:50,475
What do you know?

413
00:31:50,476 --> 00:31:52,959
Let me tell you.
In that 13 Punishments Lianyu Pagoda,

414
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:56,719
all 13 floors are full of vicious beasts,
monsters and evil spirits.

415
00:31:56,720 --> 00:31:58,719
Devilish formations
that erode the soul and heart.

416
00:31:58,720 --> 00:32:01,958
The one who is punished has to
climb from the bottom to the top

417
00:32:01,959 --> 00:32:03,439
to be able to survive it.

418
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:04,687
All these years,

419
00:32:04,688 --> 00:32:07,621
those who could survive it
are few and far in between.

420
00:32:07,622 --> 00:32:09,206
Are you courting death?

421
00:32:09,782 --> 00:32:12,791
Even though it’s rare,
it’s not impossible.

422
00:32:13,760 --> 00:32:16,386
You are a fool.
You are betting with your life.

423
00:32:19,607 --> 00:32:21,182
This won’t do.

424
00:32:25,295 --> 00:32:26,278
How about this.

425
00:32:26,279 --> 00:32:29,909
You should just escape from
the secret tunnel that I dug out.

426
00:32:29,910 --> 00:32:32,110
Don’t ever come back
to Lize Palace anymore.

427
00:32:33,080 --> 00:32:34,741
I can’t leave.

428
00:32:34,742 --> 00:32:38,129
If I leave, I’ll become
Lize Palace’s traitor.

429
00:32:38,711 --> 00:32:40,519
I’m indebted to my master.

430
00:32:40,520 --> 00:32:41,959
Even if I have broken the rules,

431
00:32:41,960 --> 00:32:44,637
I can’t escape in fear of punishment
and bring shame to him.

432
00:32:44,638 --> 00:32:49,463
Moreover, if I just run away, am
I going to hide and run forever?

433
00:32:51,058 --> 00:32:53,424
- Little Phoenix.
- Don’t worry, Brother Liu.

434
00:32:53,955 --> 00:32:56,277
Since there’s a way out from
the 13 Punishments,

435
00:32:56,278 --> 00:32:59,478
I’m going to escape using that way.

436
00:33:03,446 --> 00:33:06,392
I really don’t know what to say to you.

437
00:33:26,720 --> 00:33:29,559
Ling Long, don’t worry.
Xuan Ji will be fine.

438
00:33:29,560 --> 00:33:31,781
But she has been unconscious
for so many days.

439
00:33:31,782 --> 00:33:33,302
How can I not worry?

440
00:33:33,935 --> 00:33:35,615
What should we do now?

441
00:33:42,080 --> 00:33:43,842
I’m so hungry.

442
00:33:45,160 --> 00:33:47,533
- Xuan Ji, you are awake!
- Xuan Ji.

443
00:33:47,534 --> 00:33:49,799
- Xuan Ji.
- Little Six, keep an eye on her.

444
00:33:49,800 --> 00:33:51,845
- I’ll call for someone.
- Okay.

445
00:33:51,846 --> 00:33:53,246
Xuan Ji.

446
00:33:53,960 --> 00:33:55,743
Sixth Senior.

447
00:33:55,744 --> 00:33:58,070
You are finally awake. You scared us.

448
00:33:59,400 --> 00:34:01,039
Thank you, Sixth Senior.

449
00:34:02,094 --> 00:34:03,199
What did you say?

450
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:06,413
Aren’t you the one who pulled me out
from the water that day?

451
00:34:12,120 --> 00:34:14,518
I was so scared when I fell down that day.

452
00:34:14,519 --> 00:34:16,479
I thought I was going to die.

453
00:34:16,480 --> 00:34:19,440
Luckily, you pulled me out. Thank you.

454
00:34:20,240 --> 00:34:22,670
No. It wasn’t like that.

455
00:34:22,671 --> 00:34:24,279
That day...

456
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:25,199
- Master.
- Father.

457
00:34:25,200 --> 00:34:26,239
Xuan Ji.

458
00:34:26,240 --> 00:34:27,542
Aunt Ying Hong.

459
00:34:27,543 --> 00:34:29,013
Senior Hao Chen.

460
00:34:34,180 --> 00:34:37,479
Xuan Ji has recovered.
No need to worry now.

461
00:34:37,480 --> 00:34:39,933
See? I know that she’ll be fine.

462
00:34:40,438 --> 00:34:42,381
It’s good that she has recovered.

463
00:34:42,382 --> 00:34:44,519
I really can’t believe you!

464
00:34:44,520 --> 00:34:48,188
You don’t practise hard usually.
That’s why you couldn’t react in time!

465
00:34:48,189 --> 00:34:49,909
You made us worry.

466
00:34:49,910 --> 00:34:52,053
I’m sorry, father.

467
00:34:52,054 --> 00:34:55,199
Father, Xuan Ji did it to save me.
If you want to scold someone, scold me.

468
00:34:55,200 --> 00:34:58,101
Sect Leader Chu, Xuan Ji
was very courageous this time.

469
00:34:58,102 --> 00:35:01,468
She stepped forward bravely when
danger hits. You should compliment her.

470
00:35:02,030 --> 00:35:03,199
Junior Xuan Ji.

471
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:05,241
How’s your wound?
Do you feel uncomfortable?

472
00:35:05,983 --> 00:35:07,509
You’ve recovered well.

473
00:35:07,510 --> 00:35:10,072
But your wound is quite deep.

474
00:35:10,073 --> 00:35:12,719
Weren’t you afraid when
the sword flew towards you?

475
00:35:12,720 --> 00:35:14,599
I didn’t think that much.

476
00:35:14,600 --> 00:35:16,559
I just didn’t want Ling Long to get hurt.

477
00:35:16,560 --> 00:35:19,932
Dummy. I’m tougher than you.
A sword wound is nothing.

478
00:35:19,933 --> 00:35:22,439
Don’t do this again in the future.
It’s dangerous.

479
00:35:22,440 --> 00:35:24,685
Enough. Say no more.

480
00:35:24,686 --> 00:35:26,319
Recuperate well.

481
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:27,919
Take care of her, both of you.

482
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:29,433
We’ll be leaving first then.

483
00:35:34,262 --> 00:35:36,334
- Xuan Ji.
- Ling Long.

484
00:35:36,335 --> 00:35:38,639
Where is Si Feng? Why isn’t he here?

485
00:35:38,640 --> 00:35:41,620
You’ve been unconscious for many days.
The Flower Session has already ended.

486
00:35:42,882 --> 00:35:44,479
I was unconscious for so long?

487
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:46,931
I thought it was just a dream.

488
00:35:46,932 --> 00:35:48,759
- So, Si Feng has left?
- Yes.

489
00:35:48,760 --> 00:35:52,079
He came here every day to take care of you
but you didn’t wake up.

490
00:35:52,080 --> 00:35:54,157
In the end,
he couldn’t drag it out any longer.

491
00:35:54,158 --> 00:35:56,598
So, he went back to Lize Palace.

492
00:35:56,599 --> 00:35:58,519
I’m too useless.

493
00:35:58,520 --> 00:36:00,759
I was unconscious for so long
just because of a sword wound.

494
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:02,623
I couldn’t even bid farewell to him.

495
00:36:02,624 --> 00:36:05,910
It’s alright.
We can still meet him, right?

496
00:36:05,911 --> 00:36:07,599
- Junior Xuan Ji.
- Junior.

497
00:36:07,600 --> 00:36:09,277
First Senior, Second Senior.

498
00:36:09,278 --> 00:36:12,403
What is it? Aren’t you happy that
we are here to see you?

499
00:36:12,404 --> 00:36:14,399
Of course not. I’m very happy.

500
00:36:14,400 --> 00:36:16,959
Xuan Ji, you’ve really
changed my mind about you.

501
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:20,152
You risked your life to take a sword
for Ling Long. You were so brave.

502
00:36:20,153 --> 00:36:24,079
You don’t have any strong point usually
but you are so unselfish in critical time.

503
00:36:24,080 --> 00:36:25,686
How could you say that?

504
00:36:28,720 --> 00:36:31,046
Xuan Ji, we know that
you will be bored while recuperating.

505
00:36:31,047 --> 00:36:32,586
So, we brought you something.

506
00:36:35,566 --> 00:36:36,683
Second Junior.

507
00:36:36,684 --> 00:36:39,599
You even gave the treasure you got
when you roamed the world to her?

508
00:36:39,600 --> 00:36:43,559
Our junior is so unselfish.
Of course I have to be magnanimous too.

509
00:36:43,560 --> 00:36:46,419
Xuan Ji, I still have a lot of treasures.
I’ll show you later.

510
00:36:52,811 --> 00:36:55,822
Are you worried about Xuan Ji?

511
00:36:57,000 --> 00:36:58,399
Yes.

512
00:36:58,400 --> 00:37:02,962
Xuan Ji is so slow when
it comes to her training.

513
00:37:02,963 --> 00:37:04,599
How can I not worry?

514
00:37:04,600 --> 00:37:07,453
She never knows
what danger is since young.

515
00:37:07,454 --> 00:37:10,099
She has escaped from death so many times.

516
00:37:10,100 --> 00:37:12,828
Although it’s already very lucky that
she can grow up safely

517
00:37:12,829 --> 00:37:14,629
and I shouldn’t ask for more,

518
00:37:15,640 --> 00:37:18,639
just like how her mother took care of her

519
00:37:18,640 --> 00:37:21,527
and kept her by her side all the time
when she was still alive,

520
00:37:21,528 --> 00:37:23,569
accidents would still happen.

521
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:25,880
And her mother

522
00:37:27,080 --> 00:37:29,430
couldn’t take care of her forever too.

523
00:37:30,262 --> 00:37:31,597
From now on,

524
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:35,309
I really don’t know how to educate her.

525
00:37:35,310 --> 00:37:38,629
So, you are always so strict towards her

526
00:37:38,630 --> 00:37:42,839
because you want her to know how
to defend herself from being bullied

527
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:45,918
and be able to save herself
in a sticky situation.

528
00:37:45,919 --> 00:37:47,111
Right?

529
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:51,255
Actually, regarding Junior Xuan Ji,

530
00:37:51,256 --> 00:37:54,614
my master has different opinions
from yours.

531
00:37:54,615 --> 00:37:57,279
My master can see that
she is a talented person.

532
00:37:57,280 --> 00:37:59,239
So, he asked me to request
for your permission

533
00:37:59,240 --> 00:38:01,279
to let her be my master’s disciple.

534
00:38:01,280 --> 00:38:02,600
Really?

535
00:38:04,680 --> 00:38:06,941
I wouldn’t joke about it.

536
00:38:06,942 --> 00:38:09,708
Although my master always stays
at Xuyang Peak in order to

537
00:38:09,709 --> 00:38:11,589
reinforce the barrier
of the secret ground,

538
00:38:11,590 --> 00:38:14,239
he always talks to me about matters
in Shaoyang Sect.

539
00:38:14,240 --> 00:38:16,119
Although her six senses are not developed

540
00:38:16,120 --> 00:38:19,215
and her personality
is different from others,

541
00:38:19,216 --> 00:38:22,965
she never loses her pure heart.

542
00:38:22,966 --> 00:38:24,839
Xuyang Peak will suit her well.

543
00:38:24,840 --> 00:38:27,338
And it’s suitable for her to learn
the Heartless Tactics.

544
00:38:29,319 --> 00:38:32,669
Senior Heng Yang is considered

545
00:38:32,670 --> 00:38:35,301
the most cultivated person
in Shaoyang Sect.

546
00:38:35,302 --> 00:38:36,948
Of course he has his own view.

547
00:38:37,494 --> 00:38:40,621
If she can really enter Xuyang Peak

548
00:38:40,622 --> 00:38:43,318
and become Senior Heng Yang’s
female disciple,

549
00:38:43,319 --> 00:38:47,119
she must be blessed from her past life.

550
00:38:47,791 --> 00:38:50,679
So, you agree with this suggestion?

551
00:38:50,680 --> 00:38:53,290
It’ll be my honour.

552
00:38:53,291 --> 00:38:56,678
When Xuan Ji is feeling better
after a few days,

553
00:38:56,679 --> 00:39:00,679
I’ll summon her and tell her
about this great news at once.

554
00:39:01,847 --> 00:39:03,047
Okay.

555
00:39:07,400 --> 00:39:10,725
Xuan Ji, listen to me.
Although master looks so strict,

556
00:39:10,726 --> 00:39:12,949
he worries about you the most.

557
00:39:12,950 --> 00:39:15,694
The five sects are working together
to catch Wu Tong.

558
00:39:15,695 --> 00:39:17,319
The five sects working together?

559
00:39:17,320 --> 00:39:19,159
- Isn’t that awesome?
- What’s so awesome?

560
00:39:19,160 --> 00:39:22,255
So many people are looking for him.
But they still can’t find him, right?

561
00:39:22,256 --> 00:39:26,519
If I see Wu Tong, I’ll poke a
hole through his shoulder as well.

562
00:39:26,520 --> 00:39:28,999
Let him have a taste of
what it feels like.

563
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:31,268
Ling Long, don’t be so rash.

564
00:39:31,269 --> 00:39:33,421
Look. I’m fine now.

565
00:39:33,422 --> 00:39:34,999
Just let Wu Tong go.

566
00:39:35,000 --> 00:39:36,959
Don’t provoke him anymore.

567
00:39:36,960 --> 00:39:40,324
I think Wu Tong is
narrow-minded and cruel.

568
00:39:40,325 --> 00:39:43,679
If he can injure me,
he might even kill someone one day.

569
00:39:43,680 --> 00:39:45,519
We better stay away from him.

570
00:39:45,520 --> 00:39:49,280
Why do you sound exactly like Si Feng?

571
00:39:50,513 --> 00:39:52,959
Because Si Feng told me the same thing.

572
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:54,279
He told me that

573
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:57,718
if we tie ourselves to a despicable man,
we are the one who will suffer in the end.

574
00:39:57,719 --> 00:40:00,279
I think Si Feng knows a lot of thing.

575
00:40:00,280 --> 00:40:03,233
I’m sure that he’s right.
Let’s just take his advice.

576
00:40:03,234 --> 00:40:06,894
I am your sister
but you never take my advice.

577
00:40:09,170 --> 00:40:12,399
What happened during the Flower Session?

578
00:40:12,400 --> 00:40:14,639
Si Feng withdrew from
the competition for you.

579
00:40:14,640 --> 00:40:16,765
In the end,
Senior Shi Feng from Xuanyuan Sect

580
00:40:16,766 --> 00:40:18,998
won the competition and got the flower.

581
00:40:19,520 --> 00:40:21,319
Talking about this Flower Session,

582
00:40:21,320 --> 00:40:24,199
Xuanyuan Sect is like
a new force on the rise. A dark horse.

583
00:40:24,200 --> 00:40:25,839
Xuan Ji, you didn’t see

584
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:27,879
how proud those people from
Xuanyuan Sect were.

585
00:40:27,880 --> 00:40:30,941
They just acted like
the master of all five sects

586
00:40:30,942 --> 00:40:32,762
and started to order us around.

587
00:40:33,949 --> 00:40:37,334
But Si Feng could have won.

588
00:40:37,335 --> 00:40:39,085
Because of me

589
00:40:40,440 --> 00:40:41,886
he...

590
00:40:54,183 --> 00:40:56,439
Father, you are looking for me?

591
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:58,141
Senior Hao Chen.

592
00:40:59,160 --> 00:41:01,672
Did I cause any trouble again?

593
00:41:03,366 --> 00:41:04,748
Xuan Ji.

594
00:41:04,749 --> 00:41:07,197
Do you know that everyone
was very worried about you

595
00:41:07,198 --> 00:41:08,878
when you were wounded?

596
00:41:10,175 --> 00:41:11,759
It’s my fault for being too useless.

597
00:41:11,760 --> 00:41:14,015
I made everyone worried about me.

598
00:41:14,016 --> 00:41:15,919
Then, do you want to improve yourself

599
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:18,228
so that they won’t have to
worry about you again?

600
00:41:18,229 --> 00:41:20,981
Of course. I want to become more powerful.

601
00:41:20,982 --> 00:41:24,071
Then, I’ll be able to protect
the important people around me.

602
00:41:28,070 --> 00:41:29,239
Junior Xuan Ji,

603
00:41:29,240 --> 00:41:32,268
do you want to come to Xuyang Peak
to train together with me?

604
00:41:32,269 --> 00:41:34,548
- Xuyang Peak?
- Yes.

605
00:41:35,080 --> 00:41:39,039
Master Heng Yang is willing to
take you as his disciple.

606
00:41:39,040 --> 00:41:43,388
He’s willing to train you personally.

607
00:41:43,389 --> 00:41:45,399
Master Heng Yang?

608
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:48,638
I... I’m so stupid.

609
00:41:48,639 --> 00:41:51,079
But he still wants to
take me as his disciple.

610
00:41:51,080 --> 00:41:53,413
Has he become silly from age?

611
00:41:54,598 --> 00:41:56,199
Rude.

612
00:41:56,200 --> 00:41:58,492
It’s your blessing that Master Heng Yang

613
00:41:58,493 --> 00:42:00,799
is willing to accept you as his disciple.

614
00:42:00,800 --> 00:42:06,757
I know. That’s why I said that he
should accept extraordinary disciple

615
00:42:06,758 --> 00:42:08,919
like Senior Hao Chen.

616
00:42:08,920 --> 00:42:11,813
Not a dummy like me.

617
00:42:11,814 --> 00:42:15,294
How do you know that
you are not extraordinary?

618
00:42:16,239 --> 00:42:18,237
You are different from others.

619
00:42:18,238 --> 00:42:20,399
Your six senses are undeveloped.

620
00:42:20,400 --> 00:42:23,573
Actually, that’s your inborn talent too.

621
00:42:23,574 --> 00:42:25,934
It’s something that others don’t have.

622
00:42:25,935 --> 00:42:27,735
Having no six senses

623
00:42:28,758 --> 00:42:30,445
is a good thing?

624
00:42:30,446 --> 00:42:32,557
Since God has already
chosen a path for you,

625
00:42:32,558 --> 00:42:34,827
no need to doubt yourself.

626
00:42:34,828 --> 00:42:37,869
You just need to find the right way
and train hard.

627
00:42:37,870 --> 00:42:40,470
I believe that you’ll be able to
achieve something great.

628
00:42:41,039 --> 00:42:43,589
Si Feng said the same thing too.

629
00:42:43,590 --> 00:42:46,210
Can I really become someone
who’s more powerful?

630
00:42:51,909 --> 00:42:55,189
Senior, I’m willing to go to
Xuyang Peak to train together with you.

631
00:43:21,960 --> 00:43:23,111
Xuan Ji.

632
00:43:24,902 --> 00:43:26,399
Xuan Ji.

633
00:43:26,400 --> 00:43:27,561
Xuan Ji.

634
00:43:28,280 --> 00:43:29,410
Xuan Ji.

635
00:43:29,916 --> 00:43:31,885
Si Feng, I am Ling Long.

636
00:43:32,463 --> 00:43:34,932
The sound of this thing
can really travel for miles.

637
00:43:35,840 --> 00:43:38,839
Ling Long, how is Xuan Ji now?

638
00:43:38,840 --> 00:43:42,359
I’m sorry. I forgot to tell you that
Xuan Ji is fine now.

639
00:43:42,360 --> 00:43:44,094
But she is summoned by my father now.

640
00:43:44,095 --> 00:43:46,444
I’ll tell you when she comes back, okay?

641
00:43:46,445 --> 00:43:47,839
Good.

642
00:43:47,840 --> 00:43:52,710
Ling Long, tell Xuan Ji that after
she is done, send me a message.

643
00:43:52,711 --> 00:43:54,599
I’ll wait for her.

644
00:43:54,600 --> 00:43:56,180
Don’t worry.
